  description: "collections.abc.Awaitable.__name__.__len__() == 9 — Awaitable, Generator, and Coroutine all have __name__ length 9; Awaitable(len=9) is the base of Coroutine(len=9), and Generator(len=9) is structurally parallel; verified with Python 3.14.4"
  category: identity
